html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    title Helldivers
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(href="style.css", rel="stylesheet")
  body
    table
      thead
        tr
          for cat in cats
            th(class=cat)= header(cat)
      tbody
        for wpn in weapons
          tr
            for cat in cats
              td(class=cellClass(cat, wpn))= value(cat, wpn)

    ul
      li Reload is measured from when reticle disappears to when it comes back. Not all weapons had a reticle. Timing may be off by up to 0.1s.
      li Spare is in the format (Starting mags) / (Max mags)
      li Pickup is in the format (Supply box) / (Ammo box)

